  "time_ut": 1656564701,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b85\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd  \u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "New practice in schools from next week in the East",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to the current fuel shortage problem, it has been decided to hold classes in the Eastern Province for three days from next week.",
        "Except Monday, Friday, Tuesday, Wednesday and Thursday, schools will be held as usual.",
        "The Governor made this announcement at a Zoom technical meeting with the Eastern Provincial Secretary of Education, Provincial Director of Education and Zonal Directors of Education.",
        "The respective Zonal Directors of Education have passed this information to the Principal Teachers in their Zonal Intelligence Group WhatsApp Group.",
        "The Governor requested that the teachers and students should be fully mobilized on Tuesdays, Wednesdays and Thursdays to provide full instruction to the students and carry out full-scale learning and teaching activities. Parents should co-operate in this.",
        "Meanwhile, the teacher unions are planning to carry out some misguidance. Principals and teachers should cooperate in this matter regardless.",
        "The governor said he would talk to the three district governors if possible to help resolve the fuel issue.",
        "Top officials of the Transport Board were also present. Public transport has also been arranged for schools with transport problems.",
        "The three-day school will run from Monday, July 4 to Friday, July 8.",
        "Also, it was said in the meeting that after that how to run the school will be announced in detail later."
      ],
